        Color Target Generation & ICC/ICM Profiling           
======================================================================

Automated ArgyllCMS GUI for calibrating printers on macOS, Linux, and Windows.
A selection of targets is provided as examples in the folder Pre-made_Targets.
These are adapted for use with X-Rite ColorMunki Photo, i1Studio and i1Pro.
Modify target charts and command arguments in .ini file.

